Generic single-database configuration with async support for Ybryx Capital backend.

## Creating a new migration

```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description of changes"
```

## Applying migrations

```bash
# Upgrade to latest
alembic upgrade head

# Downgrade one revision
alembic downgrade -1

# Show current revision
alembic current

# Show migration history
alembic history
```
